Constructor Detail

SecondaryLeaf

public SecondaryLeaf(int bucketFactor)
Creates a secondary leaf (we don't have the reference list). It initializes the reference list by placing dead references equal to bucketFactor parameter. Then it assigns the bucketFactor parameter's value to the bucketFactor field and initializes all other fields with the default values.

Parameters:
bucketFactor - The bucket factor's value.

SecondaryLeaf

public SecondaryLeaf(int bucketFactor,
                     LinkedList<Reference> references)
Creates a secondary leaf (we do have the reference list). It initializes the reference list from the references parameter. Then it assigns the bucketFactor parameter's value to the bucketFactor field, the size of references parameter to the indexOfNextReferenceToBeFilled field and initializes all other fields with the default values.

Parameters:
bucketFactor - The bucket factor's value.
references - A LinkedList of references.
